# Zeta Capital Website Redesign Plan

Recreating [Zeta Capital](https://zetacapital.my/) with 99% accurate content and a premium, high-tech redesign.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Design Theme**: I propose a "Next-Gen Software Agency" aesthetic—Deep Dark Mode with Radiant Blue accents, Glassmorphism, and high-density technical layouts.
> **Content Sync**: I will use the exact language from the live site but structured for better scannability. 
> **Asset Generation**: I will generate premium software-themed images to replace any generic screenshots.

